      "description": "Construct geometry: 7.5 mm outer diameter non-cannulated pedicle screw, 45 mm vertebral body block spacing per ASTM F1717. Applied load range: 0–2500 N axial compressive force with 10 mm moment arm. Displacement range: 0–40 mm. Material: titanium alloy Ti-6Al-4V (E = 114 GPa, yield = 880 MPa). Temperature: ambient 23 ± 2 °C. Crosshead rate: 5 mm/min quasi-static."
    },
